{"tid":1808252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術post] 講多一次 帶3套衫出街","createTime":"2020-01-02T08:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T07:28:03.000Z","uid":61886,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7ed68f09ec960ef9ac3d7caff2db748ea9028f","tid":1808252,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:58:55.000Z","msg":"眼見愈黎愈多手足比人秋後算帳<br />\n比CCTV chase到<br />\n所以希望再開post提醒各位手足<br />\n<br />\n1. Black bloc<br />\n我唔再詳細咁講<br />\n風褸+帽+面巾+黑超+冰袖+手套+背囊套+鞋套<br />\n齊依set野既人應該1/10都無<br />\n使唔使補下裝自己諗<br />\n自己執生<br />\nPS 睇下自己有無特別顯眼既特徵 eg 紋身、墨etc<br />\n<br />\n2. 換裝地點<br />\n高危行動手足請踩線<br />\n進場前後請留意cctv<br />\n其實周街都係<br />\n搵到靚位就換左先<br />\n唔好貪方便企o係街換<br />\n死硬<br />\n<br />\n3. 進場前後服裝<br />\n舉個例<br />\n進場前: 白tee 灰cap帽 黑長褲 波鞋 Superdry背囊<br />\n進場: 灰cap帽&gt;黑cap帽 / 波鞋&gt;鞋套 / Superdry背囊&gt;背囊套 / 白tee&gt;風褸<br />\n退埸: 換新tee / 換短褲 / 換cap帽 / 背囊用大紙袋裝<br />\n簡單黎講<br />\n進場 / 行動 / 退場 無一樣服飾係會相同<br />\nPS 棄唔棄裝自己決定<br />\n<br />\n4. 反跟縱<br />\n換好衫<br />\n就慢慢行下街<br />\n搭下車去遠d幫襯黃店食個飯<br />\n再行多d路消化下<br />\n<br />\n5. 屋企唔好keep太多物資<br />\n一搜屋就GG<br />\n自己諗下仲可以放邊<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"35de4b29163b10635991c7f7c0f7dca811cc86d5","tid":1808252,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"戰術post <br />\n幫手推一推"},{"pid":"6de19a7af2960d5ada0d3c95cadd9bcce731bee7","tid":1808252,"uid":302503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8508e0999c7307feebc4ea43359b1907747c985b","tid":1808252,"uid":111602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0c2fc2f6b0dc79714111dbf27f0c17cb6e26af","tid":1808252,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"50b34ee4a57db84bb23c88472eaee24c53fea34a","tid":1808252,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0